if that's what you're thinking.

30:12.085 --> 30:14.053
No, he's not.

30:14.087 --> 30:16.555
No, I mean,
if anything, she's...

30:16.590 --> 30:18.791
All right, you guys.

30:18.825 --> 30:21.327
