30:29.336 --> 30:30.970
All right.

30:31.004 --> 30:32.905
Well, you did wait,

30:32.940 --> 30:36.042
and I would like you
to wait a while longer.

30:36.076 --> 30:38.244
Well, we don't want
to wait a while longer.

30:38.278 --> 30:40.646
Then, I guess,
if that's what you want to do,

30:40.681 --> 30:43.049
that's what you want to do.

30:43.083 --> 30:46.085
