to get tested, Mom.

31:00.968 --> 31:02.868
I mean, when I had sex,
we used a condom,

31:02.903 --> 31:05.171
and when he had sex,
he used a condom, too, right?

31:05.205 --> 31:07.773
Uh, yeah.
