where it should just
be the two of us.

31:11.478 --> 31:15.114
Yeah, that's fine with me.
And Grace and I
can maybe talk later.

31:15.148 --> 31:17.650
And, Grant, I'm always available
to talk to you as well.

31:22.522 --> 31:23.823
What?

31:23.857 --> 31:25.491
