a couple of times.

34:08.788 --> 34:10.556
Yeah, I know.
I couldn't text you back.

34:10.590 --> 34:12.558
Why is that?
Still busy with your survey?

34:12.592 --> 34:14.693
No, no.
I'm not doing that anymore.

34:14.728 --> 34:16.862
I did what you asked me to do.
I got tested.

34:16.897 --> 34:19.598
Oh.
That's it-- "Oh"?

34:19.632 --> 34:22.534
I would've gone with you
if I had known
you were going to do that.

34:22.569 --> 34:25.571
I didn't want you to go with me.
I didn't want anyone
to go with me.

34:25.605 --> 34:27.639
