I'll let you know
when I hear something.

34:33.780 --> 34:35.380
Uh, will you hear
something tomorrow?

34:35.415 --> 34:36.882
Or the next day or whenever.

34:36.917 --> 34:38.551
I'll talk to you later.
I just got home.

34:38.585 --> 34:40.920
Okay. Uh, thanks, Ricky.

34:40.954 --> 34:43.289
Thank you for doing that. Bye.

34:43.322 --> 34:44.757
