I don't know if it'll last.

36:06.242 --> 36:07.876
No one knows that.

36:07.911 --> 36:09.978
And that is why
I'm never gonna get married.

36:10.013 --> 36:11.847
Maybe you will,
and maybe you won't.

36:11.881 --> 36:14.116
